Package org.mxupdate.update.datamodel

Class Summary
AbstractAttribute_mxJPO The class is used to evaluate information from attributes within MX used to export, delete and update an attribute.
AbstractDMWithAttributes_mxJPO The class is used to handle the export / import of administration objects depending on attributes.
AbstractDMWithTriggers_mxJPO Abstract class for all data model administration objects with triggers.
AbstractDMWithTriggers_mxJPO.Trigger Class used to store informations about triggers.
AttributeBoolean_mxJPO The class is used to evaluate information from boolean attributes within MX used to export, delete and update a boolean attribute.
AttributeDate_mxJPO The class is used to evaluate information from date attributes within MX used to export, delete and update a date attribute.
AttributeInteger_mxJPO The class is used to evaluate information from integer attributes within MX used to export, delete and update a integer attribute.
AttributeReal_mxJPO The class is used to evaluate information from real attributes within MX used to export, delete and update a real attribute.
AttributeString_mxJPO The class is used to evaluate information from string attributes within MX used to export, delete and update a string attribute.
Dimension_mxJPO The class is used to export and import / update dimension administration objects.
Dimension_mxJPO.Unit The class is used to store information about a single unit of a dimension.
Expression_mxJPO  
Format_mxJPO  
Interface_mxJPO Data model interface class.
NumberGenerator_mxJPO  
Policy_mxJPO The class is used to export and import / update policy configuration items.
Policy_mxJPO.Access Access definition for owner / public definitions (depending on one state or for all states).
Policy_mxJPO.AccessFilterDouble Class used to define the access and filter double.
Policy_mxJPO.Signature Class defining a signature for a state.
Policy_mxJPO.State Class defining states of a policy.
Policy_mxJPO.UserAccessFilter Class used to hold the user access for a state.
Relationship_mxJPO Data model relationship class used to export and update relationships.
Rule_mxJPO  
Type_mxJPO Data model type class.
